data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home located in the highly desirable Valley View School District.   Upon entering, you will be greeted by a spacious living area that leads to a modern kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, and a cozy dining nook. The kitchen also boasts plenty of counter space and storage, making it perfect for entertaining friends and family.  This home also includes a convenient laundry room, providing ease and efficiency to your daily routine.   Step outside onto the large deck and take in the peaceful surroundings of the spacious back yard, complete with a wood privacy fence that offers both security and tranquility. Whether you enjoy relaxing in the sun or hosting gatherings, this outdoor space has plenty of room for all of your needs.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and see all that this property has to offer.
